name: VI. Step further
description:
Since we have been able to oppose the laws of nature and enter the second dimension, it didn’t take long to make the third dimension our goal. All we needed to do was to stand across and oppose the existing reality again.Reject any limitations. This time, however, not as timidly as before. Arrogantly we have risen to the next level of existence.

Bezmiar is ours, nobody else’s.
